The paper proposes a physical layer caching scheme for wireless adhoc networks, which involves optimizing the transmission mode and analyzing the impact of system parameters on throughput. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of cache-assisted multihop gain and cache-induced dual-layer CoMP gain, which could relate to Multimedia (cs.MM) or Performance (cs.PE) sub-categories.
